data.description: Hobby farm enthusiasts welcome! This home boasts 2.97 acres that are fully fenced with large heated out building with concrete floors, water and drain that can fit 5 additional vehicles.  Features include brand new neutral carpeting and paint throughout, lots of natural light,  eat- in kitchen plus a separate dining area for entertaining, black stainless steel appliances and granite counters. Lower level offers roomy great room and lots of privacy with options for home office/exercise space.  Attached 2 car heated garage for a total of 7 garage spaces!  Country living just a few miles from town and school!
